description:
CellSleepNodeFunction:  Records of cell sleep node function parameters for each cell, including configuration thresholds and reporting parameters at a specific time and location.  
dateTime: Timestamp of the record.  Area_Name: Geographic area of the cell. CellId: Unique identifier of the cell. Id2: Redundant cell identifier. Id3:  Ancillary identifier (likely unused). vsDataType: Data type identifier. vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format. CellSleepNodeFunction.csmEutranInterFMeasReportIncr: Increment value for interference measurement reports. CellSleepNodeFunction.csmMinHitRateForCovCell: Minimum hit rate for coverage cell. CellSleepNodeFunction.csmEutranInterFMeasReportDecr: Decrement value for interference measurement reports. CellSleepNodeFunction.csmEutranInterFMeasReportMax: Maximum value for interference measurement reports. CellSleepNodeFunction.cellSleepNodeFunctionId: ID of the cell sleep node function configuration. CellSleepNodeFunction.csmEutranInterFMeasReportMin: Minimum value for interference measurement reports.
